# AITBC v1.0.0 Release Plan — Production Readiness

## Overview

v1.0.0 is the **production readiness milestone**. It is not a feature release — it is the point at which the codebase, infrastructure, and operational practices are hardened enough to handle real user funds on the AITBC mainnet. All planned releases (v0.5.16 through v0.9.0) must be complete before v1.0.0.

**Target Date**: TBD (after v0.9.0 completion)
**Theme**: "Trustworthy Infrastructure"
**Success Criteria**: A security auditor can review the codebase and find no P0/P1 issues. All releases v0.5.16–v0.9.0 are shipped and tested.

